snippet.textDisplay:
WOW .. what a joy ride !! 

Traditional folk & strings, modern equipment, rich musical fillings & fusion composition, wonderful voices & singing ... & a huge dash of freshness. 

Makes one forget the daily vagaries of the "modern" world .. & immerse oneself back into the carefree, happy, hopeful, optimistic pre-internet 80s (even if this 'fusion' is only a decade old)

I've listened to this tonic of freshness at least a few hundred times over the decade .. but ventured to thank it in the comments only today.

This .. & 'Garaj Baras' fusion .. are my routine mental health potion.

Thanks, from Pune
